This file contains information about all libraries Listaller needs to run and to compile:

=== Build dependencies ===
Listaller needs the following modules to compile for Qt4, GTK2 and NoX:

 * Lazarus >=0.9.28
 * FPC Compiler >= 2.4.0
 * GTK2 development libraries
 * libqt4intf
 * Qt4 core >= 4.5
 * SQLite3
 * GLib 2.0 or higher
 * PackageKit >= 0.5.4
 * PackageKit GLib2 module
 * GNU Gettext

=== Dependencies ===
Listaller needs the following packages to run:

General:
 * xdg-utils
 * lsb-release
 * packagekit >= 0.5.4
 * apt-file [only on APT based distributions]

GTK2 version:
 * libc6
 * libglib2.0-0
 * libgtk2.0-0
 * libpango1.0-0
 * libsqlite3-0
 * libx11-6
 * gksu
 * gnome-packagekit [optional]

Qt4 version:
 * libc6
 * libsqlite3-0
 * kdesudo
 * packagekit >=0.4.6
 * libqt4intf
 * kde-icons-oxygen
 * kpackagekit [optional]
